                        <interp inst="t18480131-name-433" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS WITHERS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, N</hi> 211.) I produce a certificate of Bram<lb></lb>mell's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 5th April</hi>, 1847, <hi rend="italic">having been before convicted, and confined six months</hi>)—he has been here four times.</p>
               <p>
